title: Garena Free Fire, 53 other Chinese apps banned by Indian govt in fresh move: Full list here - India Today
content: Garena Free Fire, 53 other Chinese apps banned by Indian govt in fresh move: Full list here  India TodayView Full coverage on Google News
description: The Indian government has banned 54 new apps, including Garena Free Fire, saying that it has the “Power to issue directions for interception or monitoring or decryption of any information through any computer resource.”
